lgebende Hauptrolle. 2018 spielte sie neben Antonio Banderas eine der Hauptrollen in Jenseits der Realität. 2019 wirkte sie in einer Episode der US-amerikanischen Fernsehserie Tom Clancy’s Jack Ryan mit. Im selben Jahr folgte eine Hauptrolle im russischen Actionfilm Coma.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Lyubov Aksyonova nasceu em 15 de março de 1990 em Moscou, RSFSR, URSS como Lyubov Pavlovna Novikova. Ela é uma atriz, conhecida por Coma (2019), Byvshie (2017) e Guardians of the Night (2016). Ela é casada com Pavel Aksyonov desde fevereiro de 2013.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"柳博夫·阿克肖诺娃于1990年3月15日出生于苏联莫斯科，原名柳博夫·巴甫洛夫娜·诺维科娃。她是一位女演员，以《昏迷》（2019 年）、《Byvshie》（2017 年）和《夜之守护者》（2016 年）而闻名。自2013年2月以来，她与Pavel Aksyonov结婚。","name":"柳波芙·阿克肖诺娃","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"柳博夫·阿克肖諾娃於 1990 年 3 月 15 日出生於蘇聯莫斯科，原名柳博夫·巴甫洛夫娜·諾維科娃。她是一位女演員，以《昏迷》（2019 年）、《Byvshie》（2017 年）和《夜之守護者》（2016 年）而聞名。自 2013 年 2 月以來，她與 Pavel Aksyonov 結婚。","name":"柳波芙·阿克肖諾娃","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Lyubov Aksenova","primary":false}}]}},"tv_54155_credits":{"at":1773689201248,"data":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":79510,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Esmé Creed-Miles","original_name":"Esmé Creed-Miles","popularity":2.5125,"profile_path":"/hmGkEC4OWsyDe7ZGVkZ7e1RjViD.jpg","character":"Hanna","credit_id":"5c33675e9251413e6a6bec35","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":175826,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Mireille Enos","original_name":"Mireille Enos","popularity":1.3815,"profile_path":"/qwRuttL3lM5ZwBQ3Uoz4JUcoRFA.jpg","character":"Marissa Wiegler","credit_id":"5c33678cc3a3680b8ca87a58","order":1},{"adult":false,"